# Persistent runtime state — bind-mounted to /data inside the container.
# Contains disk.img (up to 256 GB), OpenCore.img (~512 MB), recovery.img
# (~3.2 GB), serial logs, runtime sockets. Operator-supplied per host,
# never committed.
data/

# Legacy: prior layout used ./volumes/ for the same purpose. Still gitignored.
volumes/*.img
volumes/*.qcow2

# Operator-local boot outputs — per-boot serial logs + QEMU HMP/QMP sockets.
logs/
run/

# Private working notes — live in private gitea (pq/mos)
.claude/
DISCOVERY.md

# Local QEMU/libapplegfx-vulkan source/build trees (downloaded by build-phases
# Dockerfiles, but never committed). Multi-GB; recreated on `docker build`.
qemu-10.2.2*/
qemu-build/
qemu-*.tar.*
mos-qemu*/
libapplegfx-vulkan*/

